---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { baseUrl } from '../utils/base.ts';
---

<Layout title="UOMP - User-Owned Memory Protocol" switchHref={`${baseUrl}en/`}>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none;">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">
      <div class="ey-dot"></div>
      Draft-00 · 开放协议草案
    </div>
    <h1>
      你的记忆，<br/><em>由你授权。</em>
    </h1>
    <p>
      UOMP 让用户能够按会话、按标签、按范围临时授权 AI Agent 访问个人记忆数据——记忆留在本地，权限随时可撤销。
    </p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href={`${baseUrl}spec/`} class="btn-h1">阅读规范 →</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/0xaicrypto/uomp" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-h2">GitHub 讨论</a>
    </div>

    <div class="window-wrap">
      <div class="window">
        <div class="window-bar">
          <div class="window-dots">
            <div class="window-dot r"></div>
            <div class="window-dot y"></div>
            <div class="window-dot g"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="window-url">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6B7280" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect x="5" y="11" width="14" height="10" rx="2"/>
              <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
            </svg>
            uomp run ./examples/calendar-agent
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="window-body">
          <video autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata" width="100%">
            <source src="/demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            你的浏览器不支持视频播放。
          </video>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stats-bar">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-val">本地优先</span>
          <span class="stat-lbl">数据保留在用户设备</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-val">最小授权</span>
          <span class="stat-lbl">按 tag / key 精确控制</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-val">短期会话</span>
          <span class="stat-lbl">JWT Capability Token</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-val">可审计</span>
          <span class="stat-lbl">每次访问记录日志</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sec-eyebrow">
        <div class="sec-num">01</div>
        <span class="sec-tag">为什么需要 UOMP</span>
      </div>
      <h2>数据留在本地，<br/><em>授权交给你。</em></h2>
      <p>
        当今 AI Agent 需要访问大量个人数据才能提供个性化服务，但现有方案往往要求用户将数据上传至第三方服务器。这导致用户失去对数据的控制，Agent 可能长期保留数据，且用户难以审计访问行为。
      </p>
      <p>
        UOMP 改变这一现状：记忆数据始终保留在用户本地，Agent 只能获得临时、最小化、可审计的访问权限。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sec-eyebrow">
        <div class="sec-num">02</div>
        <span class="sec-tag">核心原则</span>
      </div>
      <h2>四个原则，<br/><em>一个目标。</em></h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>用户主权</h3>
          <p>记忆数据始终由用户拥有和控制，不迁移到 Agent 提供商。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>最小授权</h3>
          <p>按标签（Tag）或键（Key）精确授权，未授权数据默认不可访问。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>会话隔离</h3>
          <p>每个授权绑定到独立 Session，会话结束或撤销后立即失效。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
              <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="13" x2="16" y2="13"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="17" x2="16" y2="17"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>可审计</h3>
          <p>所有访问行为记录审计日志，用户可追踪 Agent 查看了什么。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sec-eyebrow">
        <div class="sec-num">03</div>
        <span class="sec-tag">工作流程</span>
      </div>
      <h2>五步完成，<br/><em>一次授权。</em></h2>
      <div class="diagram">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 720 260" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="UOMP 工作流程图">
          <defs>
            <marker id="arrowhead-zh" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="7" refX="9" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
              <polygon points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7" fill="#0A0A0A" />
            </marker>
          </defs>
          <rect x="260" y="20" width="440" height="220" rx="12" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#9CA3AF" stroke-width="2" />
          <text x="480" y="45" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6B7280" font-size="12" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif">用户本机 / User Host</text>

          <rect x="20" y="100" width="110" height="60" rx="8" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" />
          <text x="75" y="135" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A0A0A" font-size="13" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-weight="600">Agent</text>

          <rect x="300" y="60" width="120" height="44" rx="8" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" />
          <text x="360" y="87" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A0A0A" font-size="13" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-weight="600">uomp CLI</text>

          <rect x="560" y="60" width="120" height="44" rx="8" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" />
          <text x="620" y="87" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A0A0A" font-size="13" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-weight="600">Auth Service</text>

          <rect x="300" y="170" width="120" height="44" rx="8" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" />
          <text x="360" y="197" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A0A0A" font-size="13" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-weight="600">Memory Guard</text>

          <rect x="560" y="170" width="120" height="44" rx="8" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" />
          <text x="620" y="197" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0A0A0A" font-size="13" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-weight="600">Memory Store</text>

          <line x1="130" y1="115" x2="300" y2="90" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead-zh)" />
          <text x="210" y="95" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6B7280" font-size="10" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif">1. uom.json</text>

          <line x1="420" y1="82" x2="560" y2="82" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead-zh)" />
          <text x="490" y="75" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6B7280" font-size="10" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif">2. 授权</text>

          <line x1="620" y1="104" x2="130" y2="145" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead-zh)" />
          <text x="380" y="155" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6B7280" font-size="10" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif">3. Capability Token</text>

          <line x1="130" y1="155" x2="300" y2="192" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead-zh)" />
          <text x="210" y="185" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6B7280" font-size="10" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif">4. HTTP + Token</text>

          <line x1="420" y1="192" x2="560" y2="192" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowhead-zh)" />
          <text x="490" y="215" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6B7280" font-size="10" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif">5. 按 scope 过滤</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>发现 Agent</strong>：用户在 Agent 市场（如基于 ERC8004 的 Registry）发现合适的 Agent。</li>
        <li><strong>查看声明</strong>：Agent 通过 <code>uom.json</code> 声明身份和请求的记忆范围。</li>
        <li><strong>连接并授权</strong>：用户确认授权范围，Auth Service 签发短期 Capability Token。</li>
        <li><strong>访问数据</strong>：Agent 通过 Memory Guard API 在授权范围内访问数据。</li>
        <li><strong>断开连接</strong>：会话结束或用户撤销后，Token 立即失效。</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sec-eyebrow">
        <div class="sec-num">04</div>
        <span class="sec-tag">谁应该关注</span>
      </div>
      <h2>为三类人设计，<br/><em>为一个开放标准而建。</em></h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>用户</h3>
          <p>重新掌控个人数据，明确知道哪些 Agent 访问了什么。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="10" rx="2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="15" r="1.5" fill="#0A0A0A" stroke="none"/>
              <circle cx="15" cy="15" r="1.5" fill="#0A0A0A" stroke="none"/>
              <path d="M8 11V8a4 4 0 0 1 8 0v3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Agent 开发者</h3>
          <p>通过标准协议访问用户授权的数据，无需自建数据存储。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A0A0A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M6 3v18"/>
              <path d="M18 3v18"/>
              <path d="M3 6h18"/>
              <path d="M3 18h18"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>协议研究者</h3>
          <p>参与设计一个开放、去中心化的 Agent 授权标准。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section" style="border-bottom: none;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>开始探索 UOMP</h2>
      <p>阅读协议草案，查看参考实现，或加入 GitHub 讨论，一起构建用户主权的 Agent 记忆授权标准。</p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href={`${baseUrl}spec/`} class="btn-h1">阅读规范 →</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/0xaicrypto/uomp-core" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-h2">查看实现</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
